&lt;p&gt;Psychosexual Therapist COSRT/BACP/UKCP accredited&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Sexual Health Wirral offers a fully integrated and accessible service to patients throughout Wirral, encompassing all aspects of sexual health.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are looking to recruit a qualified part-time (22.5hrs) Psychosexual Therapist to join our dynamic and innovative team. The successful candidate will have experience of working within a multi-disciplinary team offering a holistic approach to care and understand the treatment and management of psychosexual problems, including initial diagnostic assessment for those who feel they have gender dysphoria.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The successful applicant should have excellent communication skills and be able to work as part of team. They should be flexible and able to adapt to the needs of the service and have the ability to work autonomously. They will be a car driver/ owner.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;For further details / informal visits contact:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Name: Lauren Martyn&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Job title: Senior Business Support Manager&lt;/p&gt;
